{"tid":1950528,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稱「武漢肺炎」慘遭陸出征！台灣漢堡王急刪文正名　粉專狂湧「這8字」酸爆","createTime":"2020-03-30T11:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T22:51:21.000Z","uid":254183,"like":37,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6dfc3535a5a93ffecf5953c126a6952235acb2ad","tid":1950528,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:28:37.000Z","msg":"台灣漢堡王（Burger King）25日於臉書粉專分享防疫促銷方案，內容卻因提及「武漢肺炎」4字遭到陸網友抵制拒吃，大陸漢堡王急忙在29日表態「我們替漢堡王中國台灣地區說聲『對不起！』。」後就有民眾發現該則貼文先是更改為新冠肺炎後直接被下架，接著相關貼文內文全數更改為新冠肺炎，立刻引發台網友8字洗版怒酸「好的，中國武漢肺炎。」慘陷風波。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4786/4786674.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4786%2F4786674.jpg&h=b4bfbff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4786/4786673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4786%2F4786673.jpg&h=be7ab6eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲台灣漢堡王將武漢肺炎改為新冠肺炎，後直接將該貼文下架引發台網友不滿 。<br />\n<br />\n漢堡王臉書粉專「BurgerKing漢堡王火烤美味分享團」，本月25日下午1時39分貼出一則防疫促銷方案，PO文首句因大大寫著「武漢肺炎」一詞，引發大陸網友反彈抵制。對此，大陸漢堡王緊急在29日透過微博發出道歉聲明，「我們為漢堡王中國台灣地區不負責任的言論表示憤怒」，更指出已聯繫台灣漢堡王負責人，「嚴厲要求刪除相關損害大家感情的言論，漢堡王台灣地區相關負責人已緊急處理相關資訊，並深表歉意。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4787/4787103.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4787%2F4787103.jpg&h=57218e0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲漢堡王中國發出道歉聲明。（圖／翻攝漢堡王中國微博）<br />\n<br />\n後就有民眾陸續發現漢堡王將該則貼文下架，且接連的幾則PO文皆改為新冠肺炎，此舉引發台網友大大不滿，紛紛湧進粉絲團以8字洗版怒酸「好的，中國武漢肺炎」，更有人直言「看來你們漢堡王真是不考慮台灣人民的感受」、「不同公司營運那幹嘛要改成新冠肺炎，武漢肺炎就武漢肺炎阿！而且你們賣的是台灣人不是中國人」，風波持續延燒。<br />\n<br />\n對此，漢堡王目前僅表態內部已盡速討論中，今日會給予回應。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Burger King已向支那跪低</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f9a4525b7f773da6e40748da32bf1d6926254ff0","tid":1950528,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"唔食啦"},{"pid":"b6bb893193388a08689183a2516f9f10e01818a0","tid":1950528,"uid":253978,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:30:07.000Z","msg":"食m記仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e177a151bbe898beeb519d82f4d3c031fa4ef203","tid":1950528,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Burger King已向支那跪低</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1463cda03fa57d45ac42dbbfe3b1f1f850c5be7","tid":1950528,"uid":111316,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b6bb893193388a08689183a2516f9f10e01818a0","tid":1950528,"uid":253978,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:30:07.000Z","msg":"食m記仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"中資vs奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咖喱味嘅屎vs屎味嘅咖喱"},{"pid":"0a801bd4494eda3830781e90495e0462e355d5bd","tid":1950528,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1463cda03fa57d45ac42dbbfe3b1f1f850c5be7","tid":1950528,"uid":111316,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b6bb893193388a08689183a2516f9f10e01818a0","tid":1950528,"uid":253978,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:30:07.000Z","msg":"食m記仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"中資vs奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咖喱味嘅屎vs屎味嘅咖喱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif